title: Man and girlfriend file teeth to a point, worship Satan,  DEAD bodies in the backyard.

description:
A man and his girlfriend worship Satan. Police enter the filty home and find two bodies buried in the backyard. Joining Nancy Grace today to discuss this case: Ken Belkin, NY criminal defense attorney; Dr. Kendall Crowns,  Pathologist, Deputy ME Travis County Texas;Steven Lampley, Former Detective;Dr. Caryn Stark, Psychologist; and reporter Levi Page.
